ckoutservice-2`\n- **Reason**: Abnormal `client_error_ratio` and `error_ratio` spiking to P99 of `1.94`.\n- **Evidence**: Both `client_error_ratio` and `error_ratio` exhibited a `0.0` normal median spiking to `1.94`.\n\n### Analysis\nEach identified component exhibited significant metric changes indicating potential issues with Pod stability, node memory resources, storage IO under high load, and error ratios in services.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"io_util\",\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"pod_processes\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"The pod processes metric showed a noticeable change which indicated potential lifecycle instability.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_processes change ratio was significant at 0.6667.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes decreased considerably, potentially affecting multiple pods.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Fault median dropped to 9497153536.0 bytes, impacting pods including redis-cart-0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tikv\",\n      \"reason\": \"An anomaly in io_util indicated increased IO wait times, affecting database performance.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Noticeable change ratio of 0.7211.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Abnormal client_error_ratio and error_ratio spiking to P99 of 1.94.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Both client_error_ratio and error_ratio exhibited a 0.0 normal median spiking to 1.94.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
